1
00:00:01,410 --> 00:00:03,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't like this.</i></font>

2
00:00:03,490 --> 00:00:05,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I really don't like this.</i></font>

3
00:00:05,010 --> 00:00:06,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I very much do not like this.</i></font>

4
00:00:07,730 --> 00:00:11,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know I have to deliver the new weapon 
to the fortress city of Scudet,</i></font>

5
00:00:11,840 --> 00:00:15,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but that means going 
to the field of battle again.</i></font>

6
00:00:17,480 --> 00:00:19,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so bummed out.</font>

7
00:00:19,160 --> 00:00:21,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Van, look.</font>

8
00:00:22,750 --> 00:00:25,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the city closest to Scudet.</font>

9
00:00:34,070 --> 00:00:40,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like a normal city at a glance, 
but I see an awful lot of soldiers.</font>

10
00:00:40,890 --> 00:00:46,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Post-defeat, our Scuderian army probably
started using it to reorganize the troops.</font>

11
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:52,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yelenetta Kingdom's new weapon 
was incredible, wasn't it?</font>

12
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a long time...</font>

13
00:01:03,980 --> 00:01:04,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Van.</font>

14
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 11: THE ULTIMATE SQUAD'S
PROUD COUNTERATTACK</font>

15
00:02:38,010 --> 00:02:43,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 11: THE ULTIMATE SQUAD'S
PROUD COUNTERATTACK</font>

16
00:02:40,420 --> 00:02:42,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's been a long time, Father.</font>

17
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:46,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Van. I hear you have been made a baron.</font>

18
00:02:46,660 --> 00:02:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I have.</font>

19
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear you defeated a dragon.</font>

20
00:02:51,870 --> 00:02:54,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it was only a forest dragon, though.</font>

21
00:02:54,650 --> 00:02:57,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-A forest dragon?!</font>

22
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:58,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you do it?</font>

23
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:03,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even I can't defeat dragons 
of that class on my own.</font>

24
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:08,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to mobilize the full force
 of my knights to face one.</font>

25
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:11,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I defeated it with ballistae.</font>

26
00:03:11,540 --> 00:03:13,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ballistae, you say?</font>

27
00:03:13,540 --> 00:03:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impossible.</font>

28
00:03:14,830 --> 00:03:17,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is no way you could have done that.</font>

29
00:03:19,710 --> 00:03:23,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if I were totally honest, 
he probably wouldn't believe me.</i></font>

30
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:24,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Young man.</font>

31
00:03:26,410 --> 00:03:27,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Panamera.</font>

32
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:32,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? Am I interrupting 
a father-son reunion?</font>

33
00:03:33,170 --> 00:03:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

34
00:03:34,990 --> 00:03:36,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is His Majesty here, too?</font>

35
00:03:36,980 --> 00:03:40,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. He's been eagerly awaiting you.</font>

36
00:03:40,530 --> 00:03:44,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was wondering if you'd prepared 
something interesting again.</font>

37
00:03:44,450 --> 00:03:46,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well then.</font>

38
00:03:48,450 --> 00:03:49,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father.</font>

39
00:03:50,860 --> 00:03:54,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall I show you my ballistae
after I've met with His Majesty?</font>

40
00:03:54,610 --> 00:03:56,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good idea.</font>

41
00:03:56,500 --> 00:04:00,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seeing is believing, as they say.</font>

42
00:04:00,340 --> 00:04:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though if you have some bolts to hand, 
I could show him my own right now.</font>

43
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:08,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I have something better now.</font>

44
00:04:09,190 --> 00:04:10,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figured you might.</font>

45
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:12,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you sell me the new ones?</font>

46
00:04:12,940 --> 00:04:15,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I'll prepare some for you soon.</font>

47
00:04:15,330 --> 00:04:17,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can talk prices later.</font>

48
00:04:18,190 --> 00:04:21,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen to you, already touting it.</font>

49
00:04:25,340 --> 00:04:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Viscountess Cayenne.</font>

50
00:04:27,250 --> 00:04:29,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have brought Baron Van Nei Fertio.</font>

51
00:04:32,730 --> 00:04:34,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please enter.</font>

52
00:04:35,260 --> 00:04:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

53
00:04:36,730 --> 00:04:39,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impressed by His Majesty's royal guards?</font>

54
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:42,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're really intense.</font>

55
00:04:42,130 --> 00:04:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're strong, right?</font>

56
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

57
00:04:45,340 --> 00:04:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since His Majesty values military feats,
his guards are all superb warriors.</font>

58
00:04:50,460 --> 00:04:54,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although with <i>your</i> gear, you might 
still stand a chance of beating them.</font>

59
00:04:57,190 --> 00:05:00,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damn, Panamera. That was on purpose.</i></font>

60
00:05:02,910 --> 00:05:04,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's go.</font>

61
00:05:06,670 --> 00:05:09,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, regarding our strategy
 going forward,</font>

62
00:05:09,420 --> 00:05:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we'll gather Scuderia's elites together
and retake the fortress city of Scudet.</font>

63
00:05:16,900 --> 00:05:18,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any objections?</font>

64
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}COUNT BARIATT SHIROCCO FERDINATTO</font>

65
00:05:23,700 --> 00:05:27,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>That's Count Ferdinatto. Arte's father.</i></font>

66
00:05:28,050 --> 00:05:30,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He does kind of resemble her.</i></font>

67
00:05:31,910 --> 00:05:36,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aperta. Is there anything we should 
be wary of for the upcoming battle?</font>

68
00:05:36,310 --> 00:05:37,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

69
00:05:37,860 --> 00:05:41,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yelenetta's army has laid siege to Scudet
 in vain many times over the years,</font>

70
00:05:41,930 --> 00:05:44,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but this time, they took it
 in the blink of an eye.</font>

71
00:05:44,930 --> 00:05:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The number one reason for this appears 
to be their wyverns and those black balls.</font>

72
00:05:49,540 --> 00:05:51,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Black balls?</i></font>

73
00:05:51,170 --> 00:05:52,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Their new weapons, huh?</i></font>

74
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:57,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words, we can't win 
without doing something about them?</font>

75
00:05:57,380 --> 00:06:01,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. However, they use 
the wyverns to attack from above.</font>

76
00:06:01,870 --> 00:06:04,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It will prove difficult to take them down.</font>

77
00:06:06,590 --> 00:06:11,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marquis Fertio, they attacked your men
with those black balls, yes?</font>

78
00:06:11,210 --> 00:06:12,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

79
00:06:12,620 --> 00:06:15,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Scuderia's reinforcements are here!</i></font>

80
00:06:15,410 --> 00:06:17,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Take this!</i></font>

81
00:06:18,390 --> 00:06:20,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's that weapon?</i></font>

82
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:25,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Lord Jalpa! Our forces
have nearly been wiped out!</i></font>

83
00:06:25,820 --> 00:06:27,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wh-What?</i></font>

84
00:06:28,690 --> 00:06:33,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They delivered tremendous force
and decimated our army.</font>

85
00:06:36,570 --> 00:06:40,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Baron, have you come up 
with a potential strategy?</font>

86
00:06:41,260 --> 00:06:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

87
00:06:43,670 --> 00:06:46,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We just need to defeat 
those wyverns quickly,</font>

88
00:06:46,610 --> 00:06:49,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">before they can attack 
with those black balls, right?</font>

89
00:06:50,010 --> 00:06:51,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph. A ridiculous notion.</font>

90
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:53,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Such childish drivel.</font>

91
00:06:53,930 --> 00:06:57,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It'd be no problem
if we could just do that.</font>

92
00:06:54,490 --> 00:06:58,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Normally, I would say 
it's out of the question, but...</font>

93
00:06:59,540 --> 00:07:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's strange, but I think 
the baron could do it.</font>

94
00:07:04,110 --> 00:07:08,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, could we have you on the front lines 
of the operation to retake Scudet?</font>

95
00:07:08,610 --> 00:07:12,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm sorry. I have no intention
 of going to the front lines.</font>

96
00:07:13,810 --> 00:07:15,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Talking back to His Majesty?</font>

97
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:17,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe it.</font>

98
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's he <i>thinking</i>?</font>

99
00:07:18,730 --> 00:07:19,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The gall of it—</font>

100
00:07:19,710 --> 00:07:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't want to go to the front lines? 
You could earn yourself glory.</font>

101
00:07:23,510 --> 00:07:27,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know, but could I please act
 in a support capacity?</font>

102
00:07:27,260 --> 00:07:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

103
00:07:28,810 --> 00:07:30,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

104
00:07:30,470 --> 00:07:32,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I don't want to get hurt.</font>

105
00:07:33,010 --> 00:07:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

106
00:07:33,850 --> 00:07:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How selfish can you get?</font>

107
00:07:35,350 --> 00:07:37,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What an impudent brat.</font>

108
00:07:37,130 --> 00:07:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of upbringing 
did he get at House Fertio?</font>

109
00:07:41,190 --> 00:07:43,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You may be a child, 
but you're out of line.</font>

110
00:07:43,980 --> 00:07:47,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're just the lord 
of a small, remote village.</font>

111
00:07:47,110 --> 00:07:49,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should know your place.</font>

112
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:53,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father, I understand that well.</font>

113
00:07:54,230 --> 00:07:59,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, none of you higher nobles have 
even imagined what it's like to be a lord</font>

114
00:07:59,450 --> 00:08:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">earnestly defending such a small village.</font>

115
00:08:02,430 --> 00:08:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

116
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marquis.</font>

117
00:08:08,820 --> 00:08:10,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Baron, continue.</font>

118
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:13,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. In the beginning,</font>

119
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:17,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was made the lord of a tiny village
 that could easily be wiped out.</font>

120
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:20,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was accompanied there by fine allies,</font>

121
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:23,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I didn't receive
any support from my family.</font>

122
00:08:25,350 --> 00:08:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Despite that, I've worked hard 
to greatly develop my patch.</font>

123
00:08:30,430 --> 00:08:32,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even so, the village remains small.</font>

124
00:08:32,910 --> 00:08:36,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If Yelenetta Kingdom were 
to attack it while I'm away,</font>

125
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:38,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they'd stand little chance of victory.</font>

126
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:44,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But would Yelenetta even bother 
to attack such a small village?</font>

127
00:08:44,310 --> 00:08:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. They actually sent 
a reconnaissance force to take Seatoh.</font>

128
00:08:48,970 --> 00:08:53,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yelenetta is serious 
about crushing us this time.</font>

129
00:08:53,790 --> 00:08:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So they will likely try to conquer 
all the other domains on their borders.</font>

130
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:04,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. And it'd be all too simple 
to burn down such a small place.</font>

131
00:09:05,060 --> 00:09:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way.</font>

132
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:08,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do we have a way to counter this?</font>

133
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:10,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll need to strengthen my defenses.</font>

134
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:15,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just want to protect the village 
my citizens have built together.</font>

135
00:09:15,690 --> 00:09:19,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I can't afford to let myself get hurt.</font>

136
00:09:22,340 --> 00:09:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand now.</font>

137
00:09:24,810 --> 00:09:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, you make it sound like you can
 counter the Yelenetta army, baron.</font>

138
00:09:30,820 --> 00:09:33,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I believe I can.</font>

139
00:09:33,250 --> 00:09:34,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impossible.</font>

140
00:09:34,940 --> 00:09:38,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're using wyverns 
and those black balls.</font>

141
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:40,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those won't be a problem, either.</font>

142
00:09:42,780 --> 00:09:47,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty, I plan to do more 
than just support from the rear.</font>

143
00:09:47,650 --> 00:09:51,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In return for that, I'll prepare 
my new ballistae and catapults.</font>

144
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

145
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:56,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How reassuring.</font>

146
00:09:56,660 --> 00:10:01,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, let's go make these ballistae
 and catapults at once.</font>

147
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:03,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going to start on them <i>now</i>?</font>

148
00:10:03,850 --> 00:10:07,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Van, you really don't 
understand the situation.</font>

149
00:10:07,970 --> 00:10:09,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're in a race against time—</font>

150
00:10:09,610 --> 00:10:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father, allow me to show you 
in person like I promised.</font>

151
00:10:24,180 --> 00:10:26,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-How can this be?</font>

152
00:10:26,110 --> 00:10:27,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What in the world is this?</font>

153
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:28,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So quickly?</font>

154
00:10:28,650 --> 00:10:30,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What's going on here?</font>

155
00:10:30,590 --> 00:10:32,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think, Father?</font>

156
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:37,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pointless. I'm sure they're just for show
 and not all that impressive.</font>

157
00:10:38,660 --> 00:10:41,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm heading back to reorganize my army.</font>

158
00:10:48,540 --> 00:10:50,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, this is incredible.</font>

159
00:10:50,780 --> 00:10:53,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is the baron's new weapon?</font>

160
00:10:53,710 --> 00:10:57,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've created another 
sensational piece of equipment.</font>

161
00:10:57,520 --> 00:11:02,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These catapults are capable of launching 
specially made shuriken to down wyverns.</font>

162
00:11:04,130 --> 00:11:07,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think we can win 
with weapons like this?</font>

163
00:11:07,540 --> 00:11:10,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't say it's guaranteed.</font>

164
00:11:10,140 --> 00:11:12,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we've done everything we can.</font>

165
00:11:12,970 --> 00:11:17,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unless the enemy surpasses my predictions,
we have a good chance of victory.</font>

166
00:11:18,420 --> 00:11:20,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be counting on you, baron.</font>

167
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:21,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

168
00:11:23,100 --> 00:11:25,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're all dismissed for today.</font>

169
00:11:25,370 --> 00:11:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go organize your armies.</font>

170
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:29,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

171
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:34,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good work today, Lord Van.</font>

172
00:11:34,820 --> 00:11:38,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks. Did you come to pick me up?</font>

173
00:11:38,130 --> 00:11:39,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

174
00:11:39,190 --> 00:11:41,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Arte is with me, too.</font>

175
00:11:45,890 --> 00:11:47,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arte?</font>

176
00:11:47,580 --> 00:11:49,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">F-Father.</font>

177
00:11:50,410 --> 00:11:52,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You bring me such grief!</i></font>

178
00:11:56,490 --> 00:11:59,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-Is Mother doing well?</font>

179
00:12:00,730 --> 00:12:04,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, she's spending her time
 in my domain as usual.</font>

180
00:12:05,300 --> 00:12:07,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad to hear that.</font>

181
00:12:08,110 --> 00:12:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm busy preparing for war.</font>

182
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:14,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's have a longer chat 
when things settle down.</font>

183
00:12:15,290 --> 00:12:18,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. I look forward to it.</font>

184
00:12:29,270 --> 00:12:31,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arte, are you okay?</font>

185
00:12:31,670 --> 00:12:34,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're not feeling well, 
maybe you should rest.</font>

186
00:12:35,350 --> 00:12:36,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

187
00:12:36,970 --> 00:12:38,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Till, stay with her.</font>

188
00:12:38,820 --> 00:12:39,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

189
00:12:42,490 --> 00:12:44,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Arte, this way.</font>

190
00:12:48,390 --> 00:12:52,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. Can I entrust you 
with our artillery squad, Khamsin?</font>

191
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:57,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure. I have no doubt that your weapons 
are the strongest, Lord Van.</font>

192
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go prove that to everyone.</font>

193
00:12:59,460 --> 00:13:00,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

194
00:13:00,870 --> 00:13:05,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For now, we'll just have to use 
the catapults to defeat those wyverns.</font>

195
00:13:05,530 --> 00:13:09,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, the Seatoh Chivalric Order 
will defend Khamsin's squad.</font>

196
00:13:09,890 --> 00:13:11,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll help out, too.</font>

197
00:13:11,810 --> 00:13:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. That's reassuring to hear.</font>

198
00:13:15,410 --> 00:13:17,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it's finally time 
for the decisive battle.</font>

199
00:13:18,340 --> 00:13:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yelenetta easily took 
the impregnable fortress city of Scudet</font>

200
00:13:21,540 --> 00:13:25,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with the help of wyverns 
and their new weapons.</font>

201
00:13:25,140 --> 00:13:26,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That means...</font>

202
00:13:26,580 --> 00:13:32,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the age of battles being decided by the 
strength of elemental mages is at an end.</font>

203
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you believe Yelenetta possesses 
the greatest military might at present?</font>

204
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or perhaps...</font>

205
00:13:41,450 --> 00:13:44,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">this boy does, with the many
 weapons he makes.</font>

206
00:13:55,870 --> 00:13:59,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will now commence 
the operation to retake Scudet!</font>

207
00:13:59,760 --> 00:14:02,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

208
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:04,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Charge!</font>

209
00:14:05,640 --> 00:14:09,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Split into two and advance, 
just as we planned!</font>

210
00:14:10,530 --> 00:14:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our top goal in this operation to retake
 Scudet is to defeat the wyverns.</font>

211
00:14:15,690 --> 00:14:18,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's ensure we seize victory!</font>

212
00:14:18,450 --> 00:14:19,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

213
00:14:19,710 --> 00:14:20,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

214
00:14:21,260 --> 00:14:22,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kusala! Pluriel!</font>

215
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:26,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll act as a mobile unit and support
 where our ranks are thinnest!</font>

216
00:14:26,550 --> 00:14:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

217
00:14:26,940 --> 00:14:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Okay!</font>

218
00:14:28,310 --> 00:14:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seatoh Chivalric Order!</font>

219
00:14:29,790 --> 00:14:32,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our role is to defend the artillery!</font>

220
00:14:32,930 --> 00:14:34,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Advance with caution!</font>

221
00:14:34,560 --> 00:14:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

222
00:14:41,850 --> 00:14:44,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. They should be coming out soon.</font>

223
00:14:46,010 --> 00:14:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn Scuderian army.</font>

224
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:51,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They plan to split up 
and destroy the ramparts?</font>

225
00:14:51,310 --> 00:14:55,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought they'd concentrate on the gate
 and destroy that, but whatever.</font>

226
00:14:55,860 --> 00:14:57,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll just crush them.</font>

227
00:14:58,930 --> 00:15:00,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ready!</font>

228
00:15:03,310 --> 00:15:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fire!</font>

229
00:15:07,090 --> 00:15:09,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! Commence the operation!</font>

230
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:12,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ready shields!</font>

231
00:15:19,590 --> 00:15:21,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They blocked all of them?</font>

232
00:15:21,570 --> 00:15:26,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hastily made them using wood blocks, 
but they work fairly well.</font>

233
00:15:26,390 --> 00:15:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impudent brat.</font>

234
00:15:28,340 --> 00:15:30,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mages, get ready!</font>

235
00:15:36,590 --> 00:15:37,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fire!</font>

236
00:15:47,130 --> 00:15:49,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's it! Destroy those shields!</font>

237
00:15:50,230 --> 00:15:52,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-The shields won't hold much longer!</font>

238
00:15:52,560 --> 00:15:53,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sir Dee?</font>

239
00:15:56,820 --> 00:16:00,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No shield can withstand 
the assault of Yelenetta's army.</font>

240
00:16:01,670 --> 00:16:02,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

241
00:16:04,530 --> 00:16:05,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The north gate?</font>

242
00:16:08,150 --> 00:16:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did that come from?</font>

243
00:16:11,370 --> 00:16:13,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? A detached force?</font>

244
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:17,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep going and destroy the gate!</font>

245
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:19,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Storm Ruler!</font>

246
00:16:20,540 --> 00:16:22,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ice Field!</font>

247
00:16:23,450 --> 00:16:26,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fire Javelin!</font>

248
00:16:27,020 --> 00:16:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh no. They were planning this
 from the start?</font>

249
00:16:31,250 --> 00:16:34,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you fell for it so fully.</font>

250
00:16:35,020 --> 00:16:36,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're forcing it open!</font>

251
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

252
00:16:38,260 --> 00:16:40,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ice Storm!</font>

253
00:16:40,070 --> 00:16:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flame Lance!</font>

254
00:16:47,510 --> 00:16:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What the hell?</font>

255
00:16:49,990 --> 00:16:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My father and Count Ferdinatto
 are both really strong, aren't they?</font>

256
00:16:55,380 --> 00:16:58,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now! Onward into Scudet Fortress!</font>

257
00:17:02,500 --> 00:17:04,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go stop them!</font>

258
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:11,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wipe out the Scuderian army!</font>

259
00:17:14,860 --> 00:17:17,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is the Yelenetta army
that's full of elites?</font>

260
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:19,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is bad.</font>

261
00:17:19,690 --> 00:17:21,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Surround them!</font>

262
00:17:22,450 --> 00:17:24,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take this!</font>

263
00:17:25,020 --> 00:17:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Panamera!</font>

264
00:17:26,520 --> 00:17:28,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't waste this opportunity!</font>

265
00:17:39,500 --> 00:17:41,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave this area to us.</font>

266
00:17:42,390 --> 00:17:43,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

267
00:17:45,790 --> 00:17:48,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't be beaten in close combat.</font>

268
00:17:52,660 --> 00:17:55,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful of attacks from range, too.</font>

269
00:18:05,740 --> 00:18:08,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all Van's people?</font>

270
00:18:08,210 --> 00:18:10,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, we are.</font>

271
00:18:14,070 --> 00:18:15,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case...</font>

272
00:18:16,010 --> 00:18:18,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Tell them it's time!</font>

273
00:18:18,340 --> 00:18:19,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

274
00:18:19,410 --> 00:18:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damn. I didn't think
 we'd struggle this much.</i></font>

275
00:18:27,020 --> 00:18:28,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wyverns!</font>

276
00:18:28,420 --> 00:18:29,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's that many of them?</font>

277
00:18:32,060 --> 00:18:33,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're finished now!</font>

278
00:18:33,860 --> 00:18:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come, drop the black balls!</font>

279
00:18:37,230 --> 00:18:38,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Khamsin, you're up!</font>

280
00:18:38,930 --> 00:18:41,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Catapults, prepare to fire!</font>

281
00:18:41,050 --> 00:18:42,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

282
00:18:44,060 --> 00:18:45,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fire!</font>

283
00:18:58,140 --> 00:19:00,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good. Just as we planned.</font>

284
00:19:08,760 --> 00:19:10,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's still one alive!</font>

285
00:19:11,890 --> 00:19:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's enormous.</font>

286
00:19:17,140 --> 00:19:18,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, Kusala!</font>

287
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:20,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it!</font>

288
00:19:25,340 --> 00:19:27,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's not working?</font>

289
00:19:27,470 --> 00:19:29,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good. We have it pinned down.</font>

290
00:19:29,960 --> 00:19:31,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ballistae, fire!</font>

291
00:19:36,700 --> 00:19:38,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave it to me!</font>

292
00:19:38,780 --> 00:19:41,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Burn the foes before me to ash.</font>

293
00:19:42,070 --> 00:19:43,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vermilion!</font>

294
00:19:58,390 --> 00:20:02,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rejoice! The enemy's main forces, 
the wyverns, have been destroyed!</font>

295
00:20:03,660 --> 00:20:05,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We did it!</font>

296
00:20:07,160 --> 00:20:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never expected the baron's power
 would be this great.</font>

297
00:20:13,790 --> 00:20:16,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've lost. Our only choice is to run.</font>

298
00:20:16,620 --> 00:20:18,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh dearie me.</font>

299
00:20:18,910 --> 00:20:20,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where do you think you're going?</font>

300
00:20:20,850 --> 00:20:22,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just come quietly, okay?</font>

301
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:33,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father.</font>

302
00:20:33,770 --> 00:20:37,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you really okay 
leaving without seeing Van?</font>

303
00:20:44,150 --> 00:20:48,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps my beliefs were wrong.</font>

304
00:20:54,670 --> 00:20:59,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We fended off and defeated Yelenetta 
Kingdom's wyverns and black balls.</font>

305
00:20:59,950 --> 00:21:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This glory is all yours, Lord Van.</font>

306
00:21:02,670 --> 00:21:05,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All I did was issue commands
 from the rear.</font>

307
00:21:05,940 --> 00:21:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was thanks to all of your efforts.</font>

308
00:21:08,910 --> 00:21:12,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm really glad everyone came to no harm.</font>

309
00:21:12,130 --> 00:21:12,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

310
00:21:13,300 --> 00:21:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Van.</font>

311
00:21:15,410 --> 00:21:18,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We captured Yelenetta's commander.</font>

312
00:21:21,450 --> 00:21:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He should know all kinds 
of confidential information.</font>

313
00:21:26,070 --> 00:21:28,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well now, maybe you could enlighten us.</font>

314
00:21:29,800 --> 00:21:31,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was your goal here?</font>

315
00:21:36,760 --> 00:21:44,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In short, their commander says Yelenetta
Kingdom's plan was a three-pronged attack.</font>

316
00:21:45,050 --> 00:21:48,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seatoh and Scudet 
were two of those prongs.</font>

317
00:21:49,480 --> 00:21:52,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the last one is...</font>

318
00:21:52,820 --> 00:21:54,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ferdinatto County.</font>

319
00:22:00,150 --> 00:22:01,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arte's homeland.</font>

320
00:22:15,940 --> 00:22:20,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TRANSLATION: JOHN PICKETT</font>

321
00:22:20,190 --> 00:22:24,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TIMING: ANDY ELLIS
EDITING: SMR</font>

322
00:22:24,450 --> 00:22:28,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}QUALITY CONTROL: RILEY DALTON
TRANSLATION CHECK: REI MIYASAKA</font>

323
00:23:34,970 --> 00:23:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}NEXT EPISODE: EASYGOING TERRITORY DEFENSE
BY THE OPTIMISTIC LORD</font>

